********************************
*** Yellow Submarine Rootkit ***
********************************

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LICENCE
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 GPLv2

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FEATURES
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - architecture supported : amd64
 - hide itself using debug registers
 - hide files
 - hide pids

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 build and load the kernel module :
  cd kernel
  make
  insmod ylsm.ko


 configure rootkit :
  cd tools
  make
  ./ylsm_ctl -h
